import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="LBW Trust Ambassador" description="Nikhil Kulkarni as an Ambassador of The LBW Trust, a cricket-based charity supporting education across South and Southeast Asia and Australia.">

  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="page-label">Community &amp; Ecosystem</p>
    <h1>LBW Trust Ambassador</h1>
    <p class="intro">I am an Ambassador of The LBW Trust, a cricket-based charity that uses the sport to support education for underprivileged students across South and Southeast Asia and Australia.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <section class="section">
      <h2>What is the LBW Trust?</h2>
      <p>The LBW Trust is a cricket-funded charity supporting education across India, Nepal, Sri Lanka, Indonesia, and Australia. It uses cricket as a vehicle to connect donors, volunteers, and communities, funding scholarships and educational support for students who would otherwise not have access.</p>
      <p>Ambassadors include prominent international cricketers and community leaders who share the Trust's belief in sport as a force for social good.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>My role</h2>
      <p class="role-meta-block">Ambassador · 2026 – present</p>
      <p>As an Ambassador, I help raise awareness of the Trust's work, connect the charity with the Australia–India community, and advocate for its mission at the intersection of cricket, education, and social impact.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Why this matters to me</h2>
      <p>Cricket has been a thread through my life — from growing up in India to building a life in Australia. The LBW Trust brings together two things I care about deeply: the game and the belief that education can change lives. Being part of this work, alongside people who share that conviction, is a privilege.</p>
    </section>

  </div>

</Base>

